          Purple Point is a decentralized platform built on <strong>MIT</strong> and <strong>GPL</strong> open source
          infrastructure. We believe creativity, education, and community building should never have a paywall.
        </p>
        <div class="open-source-badges">
          <div class="license-badge">
            <span class="license-icon">üìú</span>
            <span class="license-name">MIT License</span>
          </div>
          <div class="license-badge">
            <span class="license-icon">üîì</span>
            <span class="license-name">GPL v3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="license-badge">
            <span class="license-icon">üåê</span>
            <span class="license-name">DeFi Native</span>
          </div>
          <div class="license-badge">
            <span class="license-icon">üíö</span>
            <span class="license-name">Forever Free</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="mission-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="mission-grid">
          <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="mission-icon">üéµ</div>
            <h3>Creative Expression</h3>
            <p>Empower artists to create, battle, and earn through music without barriers or gatekeepers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="mission-icon">üåç</div>
            <h3>Global Community</h3>
            <p>Connect urban and coastal youth across Kenya and beyond through hip-hop culture and Web3.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="mission-icon">üìö</div>
            <h3>Education First</h3>
            <p>Integrate learning through video, peace engineering, and sustainable solutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="mission-icon">üíé</div>
            <h3>Fair Ownership</h3>
            <p>Artists own their work. NFTs ensure provable ownership and royalties forever.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
