        <div class="sparkhope-banner">
          <div class="sparkhope-icon">üçÑ</div>
          <div class="sparkhope-text">
            <h3>Part of SparkHope.space</h3>
            <p>Purple Point is integrated with the SparkHope mycological innovation platform, connecting creative expression with regenerative agriculture and sustainable community development.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://sparkhope.space" class="sparkhope-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
